# Development Status

This folder is under active development.

The current work focuses on modular C applications, reusable software components, embedded processing, data structures, signal-processing pipelines, state machines, communication software, testing, debugging, and performance analysis.

The planned work will extend the collection with fixed-point DSP, real-time scheduling, deterministic memory allocation, multithreaded processing, protocol parsing, atomic operations, hardware abstraction, fault recovery, automated testing, and performance optimization.

